Hope your week is off to a good start. I'm reaching out ahead of the April 1st
renewal for Acme Manufacturing Group (Policy # PCM-2021-00447).

Please find attached the updated Statement of Values for their 15 manufacturing
and warehouse locations. A few things to flag:

  - Location 7 (Kansas City, MO) has been removed from the schedule — they
