  - Location 14 is new this year: a 42,000 sq ft facility in Spartanburg, SC
    acquired in December. Full replacement cost appraisal is attached separately
    (see Acme_Spartanburg_Appraisal_2023.pdf, to follow by end of week).
  - Building values have been updated per their internal appraisal cycle.
    Total insured value (TIV) is now approximately $47.2M across all locations,
    up from $41.8M last year.
  - They are requesting the same coverage structure: Special Form, RC basis,
