  - Acme is also asking about adding Equipment Breakdown to this renewal —
    please let me know if Pinnacle can quote that in-house or if we need to
    go to market separately.

Expiring premium was $312,400. Client's expectation is flat-to-5% increase
given no losses in the past 3 years (loss run attached separately).

Please let me know if you have questions or need anything additional. I'd like
to have an indication by March 22nd if possible.

